  Arrow: I don&#39;t think that&#39;ll work, it could be a very old listing.

  (Meanwhile)

  Deemos (thinking): If someone wants to contact me, they&#39;d probably look up my old number.

  He types his old number into his commlink and waits.

  (Meanwhile)

  Arrow dials the number.

  Deemos over comm unit: Hello. No time to waste, location.

  Arrow reads off the address of the place. Since that it was so secret, I won&#39;t tell it here. (I don&#39;t know it)

  Arrow: It worked...

